[I] An OpenPGP backend for rpm using Sequoia PGP

[T] This library provides an implementation of the rpm's pgp interface using
[T] Sequoia.

[U] https://github.com/rpm-software-management/rpm-sequoia

[A] rpm-software-management
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/archive
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
[V] 1.10.2
[P] X -----5---9 138.000

[D] 1102323da1f15dfd495379dd0f1542465df0e2fea037a78d2d843ff0 rpm-sequoia-1.10.2.tar.gz https://github.com/rpm-software-management/rpm-sequoia/archive/v1.10.2/

cargoinstopt=
hook_add postmake 5 'cp -vf target/*/librpm* $root$libdir/'
hook_add postmake 5 'cp -vf target/*/$pkg.pc $root$libdir/pkgconfig'
